eligible for financial participation under 42 U.S.C. 1396b(w)(6)(A) and
42 CFR 433.51. The office shall assist a county in making this
certification.
(c) Payments by the county fiscal body must be in the amounts:
(1) determined by sections 2 through section 4 of this chapter;
and
(2) authorized by sections 1.2 and 13 of this chapter.
